{"tid":1860873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門出現社區感染了，睇嚟占奔都命不久矣","createTime":"2020-02-04T02:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T08:25:15.000Z","uid":154872,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6931883dd741da87d90ff8cb181328df773f073b","tid":1860873,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"本澳新增1例新型冠狀病毒感染確診病例，患者為29歲女性，澳門居民。直至目前，本澳確診病例已增至9例。<br />\n<br />\n經初步調查，此患者於1月24日曾到本澳第8例確診個案家中作客並逗留約4小時，於1月25日起曾有流涕、咳嗽和發燒等症狀，其後症狀消失。昨日由衛生局追蹤接觸者時發現此個案並建議到醫院檢查，經檢測對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性，被列為本澳第9個確診個案，已被安排至隔離病房治療，目前情況一般。患者否認近期有離澳，初步考慮此病例與第8例存在傳染關係，衛生局疾病防控團隊正展開追蹤調查其流行病學史和密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\nToo late, my time has come,<br />\nsends shiver down my spine, body's aching all the time.<br />\nGoodbye, everybody, I've got to go,<br />\ngotta leave you all behind and face the truth<br />\n<br />\nMama, oooh~~~~~~~~<br />\nI don't wanna die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI sometimes wish I'd never been born at all"},{"pid":"d27e9c7f4eb328ab2949de3155af7619b56156fc","tid":1860873,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:09:25.000Z","msg":"queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96abf04c98b9ce70360e5f90a1b683786087ab3","tid":1860873,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:09:56.000Z","msg":"預備左帛金"},{"pid":"1fecf6a6b22ea0fca71f3e80f7f31e51b8869b0f","tid":1860873,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a96abf04c98b9ce70360e5f90a1b683786087ab3","tid":1860873,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02:09:56.000Z","msg":"預備左帛金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T02